# CGFloat.NativeType

**Type Alias**

The native type used to store the `CGFloat`.

## Declaration

```swift
typealias NativeType = Double
```

## Discussion

The native type used to store the [doc://com.apple.corefoundation/documentation/CoreFoundation/CGFloat-swift.struct], which is [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/Float] on 32-bit architectures and [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/Double] on 64-bit architectures.
